{"tid":717419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"距離「支爆」又近一步？","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T04:30:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"881482e557a373209458425a3216ae556be84c41","tid":717419,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180531/large/1527759717_7a89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F1527759717_7a89.jpg&h=2326bc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 所謂「支爆」，意指中國經濟爆煲，是一班「連登仔」最期待的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n以目前內地經濟情況，斷言支爆似乎尚早，不過一些相對細微的債務違約事件，則值得投資者們關注。<br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》報道，曾經計劃牽頭以402億元「天價」買起長實地產（1113）旗下中環中心的中國國儲能源，竟然未能償還一筆於今年5月11日到期的三年期債券，本金為3.5億美元（約27.3億港元）。這次違約，同時導致公司另外兩筆分別於2021年及2022年到期、共6.55億美元（約51.1億港元）的債券違約條款觸發。<br />\n<br />\n另外，內地一家主力推動公私營合作模式（PPP）項目的上市公司東方園林（002310），上周初計劃發行10億元（人民幣・下同）公司債券，結果認購規模只有5000萬元，僅得原先計劃的5%，反應非常冷淡，公司股價一周內重挫兩成，最終公司聲稱有重大事項而臨時停牌。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗內地債務事件，雖然規模不大，但或反映中國債務問題已開始浮現。過去中國政府容忍金融機構以表外方式隱藏不良資產，加上政府濫印鈔票，廣義貨幣供應（M2）急速增長，讓這些不良資產容易「吊命」。不過，隨著美國不再印錢量化寬鬆兼逐步加息，中國面對兩難問題：繼續大開印鈔機則會令人民幣大幅貶值，加速資金外流，不利經濟增長；減少印鈔，不良資產「被斷奶」，違約機會迅速攀升。當越來越多國內債券爆煲，就有機會出現「骨牌效應」，投資者憂慮債券資產質素而紛紛拋售，結果，企業更難借錢。<br />\n<br />\n中國最終選擇「去槓桿」路線，要求銀行處理表外資產，希望債務爆煲在可控範圍之內，但能否有效控制仍屬未知之數，加上內地傳統上6月流動性較為緊張，對息口敏感的高槓桿行業，如融創（1918）及恒大（3333）等內房股，周三都以急跌做回應。<br />\n<br />\n一年又到六絕月，小心提防萬事穩。<br />\n<br />\n徐風<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180531/58261260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F58261260&d=JgBlPjUZD%2FMEGfzcS7QfNFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=7ad39c34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180531%2F58261260&h=06ae8c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180531/58261260</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3a9cf738302d1c29289562d7b3c72bf51f0c51","tid":717419,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4427aca3a4744bcd743e8495a6db6a5b5c30017a","tid":717419,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"曾經計劃牽頭以402億元「天價」買起長實地產（1113）旗下中環中心的中國國儲能源，竟然未能償還一筆於今年5月11日到期的三年期債券，本金為3.5億美元（約27.3億港元）。這次違約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d997c98e43c8a3346d317b6051b15e4659db45b0","tid":717419,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s33.postimg.cc/r1b32qlxb/CLOCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs33.postimg.cc%2Fr1b32qlxb%2FCLOCK.jpg&h=dddc01bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faaf4d3fe24de65874d4c8611ed99d6518d31bbc","tid":717419,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509857469_cc84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509857469_cc84.jpg&h=d7962e3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0a68a5315745153708374efe4c79e284bb3b445","tid":717419,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4427aca3a4744bcd743e8495a6db6a5b5c30017a","tid":717419,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"曾經計劃牽頭以402億元「天價」買起長實地產（1113）旗下中環中心的中國國儲能源，竟然未能償還一筆於今年5月11日到期的三年期債券，本金為3.5億美元（約27.3億港元）。這次違約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"長實又重現Orange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴賣平買中環中心"},{"pid":"c18b895af1d385ef36b43844e7e438c370c493af","tid":717419,"uid":17765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"2015年佢本來爆咗鑊<br />\n只係土共勝在夠無恥<br />\n做啲美國政府都唔敢做嘅招數救市啫"},{"pid":"e511081d327ee74867c7ae596cb7f1b1bc6297f3","tid":717419,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a68a5315745153708374efe4c79e284bb3b445","tid":717419,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4427aca3a4744bcd743e8495a6db6a5b5c30017a","tid":717419,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"曾經計劃牽頭以402億元「天價」買起長實地產（1113）旗下中環中心的中國國儲能源，竟然未能償還一筆於今年5月11日到期的三年期債券，本金為3.5億美元（約27.3億港元）。這次違約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"長實又重現Orange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴賣平買中環中心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"真係好撚勁！"},{"pid":"d5c05f9e322dbb0287a30eb7ff81f2bdb070adbf","tid":717419,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國今年債務違約　恐歷來最多</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市場對內地的憂慮，蔓延至中國債務，並恐防炸彈會再爆煲，這對人民幣匯價雪上加霜。《彭博》數據顯示，今年頭六個月，國內新的違約公募債券已達去年全年的九成，規模至少165億元人民幣。預計今年可能為中國有史以來最大違約年，單計上半年已經有至少17宗債券違約，比2015年全年的7宗違約多出逾一倍。<br />\n違約後未兌付達663億<br />\n<br />\n中國政府網公佈，新一屆國務院金融穩定發展委員會在前日成立並召開會議，研究部署防範化解重大風險，會議由國務院副總理劉鶴主持。會議公告指，中國完全具備打贏重大風險攻堅戰和應對外部風險的諸多有利條件。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當局派定心丸，但人民銀行數據顯示，截至2018年5月底，中國公司信用類債券違約後尚未兌付的金額663億人民幣。針對今年的違約潮，中信證券分析師呂品表示，之前主要是國企和過剩產能違約，大家不是很擔心這些企業會真的倒閉，而今年以民企為主，更加複雜化深度化，「從違約數量和金額上看，今年肯定會超過2016年，成為史上違約最大年。」<br />\n<br />\n中誠信李詩分析指，今年新增違約個案，集中在交易所公司債發行人，主因是2015年公司債發行規模大幅擴張，後遺症便在今年展現，密集的債務到期或回售，導致個別償債現金流嚴重不足的企業的兌付風險陸續暴露，發生實質性違約。涵蓋149家中國發行人的ICE美銀美林指數顯示於五月底，垃圾等級的公司債平均價格跌至95.2，目前有62隻債券價格低於95，反觀年初時只有6隻，現為兩年高位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180704/20439837\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F20439837&d=JgBlPjUZD%2FMEGfzcS7QfNFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b029583a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F20439837&h=da0a9e89\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180704/20439837</a>"},{"pid":"09d5803cfbfb2b55a8115ac0a6c47b7043a0feea","tid":717419,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04c9b74251a076d89c61ec5a8678cc112be5ace","tid":717419,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"爆到幾時"},{"pid":"cdcc4bc4b40bee35cd4cb466230b3d02c57614c7","tid":717419,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076f1c4adc628a4da15f7f04f06b1016510bf748","tid":717419,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f77ccae08d7aab1ed098661a0567d7bb170a50","tid":717419,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"咁玩邊可能唔爆"},{"pid":"aa20bb987b7fc5f6c028f47414975e3e57e91f56","tid":717419,"uid":58413,"like